<LEFT><BOLD>Ascended master:

One who has mastered time and space, gained mastery of the lower self and reunited with God (God’s consciousness) through the ritual of the ascension. Lightbearers have risen in every age from every culture and religion and become ascended masters of the Great White Brotherhood. They inhabit the planes of Spirit, the kingdom of God.
<LEFT><BOLD>Ascension:

The ritual whereby a soul permanently reunites with their higher self, the Spirit of the living God within them. The ascension is the victorious conclusion of the soul’s journey in time and space, ending the rounds of karma and rebirth. It is the soul’s return to God’s consciousness and is the goal of life for all lightbearers.
<LEFT><BOLD>Body of God:
All lightbearers and saints in heaven and on earth. See mystical body of God.
<LEFT><BOLD>Brotherhood of light (or the Great White Brotherhood):

A spiritual order of saints and adepts who have reunited with the Spirit of the living God and are part of the heavenly hosts. The word “white” doesn’t refer to race but to the white light surrounding their forms. The Brotherhood also includes certain unascended students of the ascended masters.
<LEFT><BOLD>Cosmic hierarchy (or hierarchy):
The universal chain of God-free beings who have each chosen and personalized various attributes and aspects of God’s infinite Selfhood.
<LEFT><BOLD>Fallen ones:
Rebel angels who fell from heaven long ago, and those on earth who have followed after them and chosen the path of darkness.
<LEFT><BOLD>False hierarchy:
The hierarchy of darkness, aka the sinister force, who pose as cosmic hierarchy in an effort to lead lightbearers on the wrong path and steal their light.
<LEFT><BOLD>Guru:
Spiritual teacher who has gained self-mastery and guides students on the true path to soul freedom.
<LEFT><BOLD>Inner levels:
Levels or planes of frequencies beyond the physical plane which is visible to us.
<LEFT><BOLD>Lightbearer:
One who bears God’s light, and works for the victory of this light by defending the truth and honor of God in everyone.
<LEFT><BOLD>Mystical body of God:
the community of Light on earth and in heaven. It consists of all lightbearers in all universes.
<LEFT><BOLD>Twin flames:

Masculine and feminine halves of a divine whole created by God. Twin flames share a spiritual blueprint and destiny that is eternal and unique in cosmos. It is a far deeper relationship than soul mates who share a mission for a time, or partners brought together by karma.
